# Transcoding Cache System
Cache transcoded video segments in storage to avoid redundant transcoding operations. Check for existing cached segments before transcoding and stream cached content when available.

## Test plan / verification steps
```bash
# Priority: Automated tests with vitest
cd services/jit-transcoding

# Run specific cache-related test files
npx vitest run server.test.ts --reporter=verbose
npx vitest run cache.test.ts --reporter=verbose  # New test file for cache functionality
npx vitest run storageProvider.test.ts --reporter=verbose  # Storage provider expiry tests

# Run existing transcoding tests to ensure no regressions
npx vitest run --reporter=verbose

# Optional manual verification (if needed)
npm run dev
# Test cache miss (first request)
curl "http://localhost:3001/api/v1/transcode/low?url=https://example.com/video.mp4&start=0" -o segment1.mp4
# Test cache hit (second request) 
curl "http://localhost:3001/api/v1/transcode/low?url=https://example.com/video.mp4&start=0" -o segment2.mp4
# Verify identical: diff segment1.mp4 segment2.mp4
```

