**📁 Cache Path Structure:**
- **Format**: `cache/transcoded/{hashedUrl}/{preset}/{hashedStartTime}-{startTimeMs}.mp4`
- **URL Hash**: Organizes by video source (16 chars)
- **Preset Directory**: Separates quality levels (low/medium/high)
- **Hashed Start Time**: Non-sequential for optimal cloud storage distribution (8 chars)
- **Readable Start Time**: Easy debugging (shows exact millisecond)
- **Example**: `cache/transcoded/abc123def456/low/xyz789ab-0.mp4`

